517
00:23:42.600 --> 00:23:43.880
You're just gonna leave it here?

518
00:23:46.689 --> 00:23:49.210
Ingrid. something on your mind?

519
00:23:50.250 --> 00:23:51.250
Nothing.

520
00:23:51.470 --> 00:23:52.570
I'm good tonight.

521
00:23:53.770 --> 00:23:54.770
