814
00:37:50.519 --> 00:37:51.619
No idea.

815
00:37:52.000 --> 00:37:53.179
They're stepping back.

816
00:37:53.779 --> 00:37:55.540
A minority partnership.

817
00:37:56.680 --> 00:38:01.000
