822
00:38:14.779 --> 00:38:16.039
I'm looking for a reason.

823
00:38:16.819 --> 00:38:17.819
Congratulations.

824
00:38:18.299 --> 00:38:19.679
I'll arrange a meet for you two.

825
00:38:23.300 --> 00:38:23.897
Ingrid?

